Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:44.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 虽然这般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:56.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回忆也会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被时间之沙掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:04.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而变得暧昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:11.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}说着「命运」这词是如此廉价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而与我一同开怀大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:21.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:26.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定会将自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:29.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐渐忘却在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}与你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也请留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成为无法集齐的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:44.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那无法寻觅的最后一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:55.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,600)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
